parameters:
\n<Ameria>"No...! No way! We can't just leave Roselitte behind and run
away!"
\n<Lyric>"...Just do as I say, and run away now."

\n<Lyric>"Calm down and think about it. If Roselitte hadn't stopped
us, what do you think would have happened to us by now?"

\n<Lyric>"Besides, I already told you. We need to report this to
Annabern quickly. If we don't, a lot of people will die. Are
you okay with that!?"

\n<Ameria>"Then you should run away, Lyric. I'll stay behind and save
Roselitte!"

\n<Lyric>"No matter what you say, no matter how many people may die,
since 'that time', I've decided to protect you."
\n<Lyric>"...So we're going to run away. Okay?"
\n<Ameria>"...I understand. Yes. With those words, I've... decided."

\n<Lyric>"Wha... What!? Why does it end up like that!? Were you even
listening to me!?"

\n<Ameria>"...Thank you. I'm really happy to hear Lyric's feelings. I
love you, Lyric."

\n<Ameria>"But you see, I feel the same way. I don't want Roselitte to
die. This time for sure... This time for sure...!"

\n<Ameria>"This time for sure I'll save her! Me too! That time!
Definitely! I decided that I would save her!"

\n<Ameria>"Roselitte tried to rely on me! She needed me! She tried to
protect me! So I absolutely must respond to those feelings!"

\n<Ameria>"Annabern too! And Roselitte as well! I will save them
all...!!"

\n<Lyric>"...I can't deal with this. If you want to die that badly,
then do as you please."
